The '''Tritonites''' were an [[Insectoid/Legends|insectoid]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from the [[Moon/Legends|moons]] of [[Triton/Legends|Triton]]. They were followers of [[Gactimus]], and as acolytes they were a common sight in [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceports]] around the [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]],<ref name="TEA" /> offering tracts to individuals for their personal enlightenment. They operated the [[Triton Moons]], famous as checkpoints.

